{"tid":391104,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完末日時覺得好難過","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T17:25:03.000Z","uid":53272,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dde301879d0d73300867e09e09a7450a8a78032b","tid":391104,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"忍唔住再去睇埋四五卷劇透<br />\n成個世界觀其實幾慘<br />\n神為左思念故鄉創造左個人既世界<br />\n人又為左呢個神創造既自己既故鄉去弒神<br />\n最後存活既又為左呢個人類弒神後得出既自己既故鄉去殺獸(人)<br />\n<br />\n而啲女女由以前到而加都為左自己愛既人付出全部 <br />\n男主又為翻佢重視既人付出自己<br />\n點解作者要咁對佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n創造個角色後又殺左佢<br />\n明明接觸二次元想避開現實<br />\n但有時又要係入面感受到現實既殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完月色睇呢套好大反差<br />\n個心好沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個腦不停loop op同埋scarborough fair<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d738e1cb1cfe354b6a8eb91b15ab21ece50f5c5e","tid":391104,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"無人睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaffe4881f86c34d3e80bab0951294329e724a03","tid":391104,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"d2f57d439cc66f03304afc7ebb42019c13d3a678","tid":391104,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:16:52.000Z","msg":"咩戲呀 識唔識英文名？"},{"pid":"1040e212c79f15320c21216e5660d23e753eb3c0","tid":391104,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩戲呀 識唔識英文名？</blockquote><br />\n動畫黎架<br />\n全名 <br />\n末日時在做什麼？有沒有空？可以來拯救嗎？<br />\n<br />\n關英文名乜時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5307f216279fab8cc1f